<span class="font-italic">Partner</span><br />
<span class="font-italic">VDB Loi</span><br /></p>
<p>
<p>An ACCA-qualified adviser, Sivila is an expert in Cambodian taxation with over 10 years of tax consulting experience, including several years with Big 4 firm KPMG.</p>


<p>At VDB Loi, he advises on tax structuring, disputes, and controversy, and conducts tax due diligence for clients across a range of industry sectors, including financial services, telecommunications, real estate, and garment manufacturing.</p>


<p>Sivila is also an associate member of the Kampuchea Institute of Certified Public Accountants and Auditors (KICPAA).</p>
